definition: important/vital/to want/to ask for/will/going to (as future auxiliary)/may/must/(used in a comparison) must be/probably/if

sentences.english: During the installation you will be prompted to create some profiles.
sentences.chinese: 在安裝期間，系統將提示創建一些概要文件。

sentences.english: I think back over the compendium of knowledge that exists there, and it still takes my breath away.
sentences.chinese: 現在回想起存於其中的知識概要，仍舊令我爲之傾倒。

sentences.english: Does anyone have the exact schematic for the J2 amplifier?
sentences.chinese: 誰是否有J2放大器的確切的概要？

sentences.english: On top of each configuration rest several profiles.
sentences.chinese: 每個配置上面都有幾個概要文件。

sentences.english: Do not apply a non-released profile to a production model.
sentences.chinese: 不要對一個生產模型應用一個非發佈概要文件。

sentences.english: None of the conceptual design issues deals with technology standards or their implementations.
sentences.chinese: 概要設計問題不會涉及到任何技術標準或其具體實現。

sentences.english: RAS can also be extended and customized via a profile.
sentences.chinese: RAS同樣可以通過概要文件來擴展和定製。

sentences.english: You will find Enclosed an outline of my education and business training and copies of two letters of recommendation.
sentences.chinese: 有關本人學歷，業務培訓的概要連同兩封信一同呈上。

sentences.english: This is useful for the user-created profiles as well.
sentences.chinese: 這對用戶創建的概要文件來說十分有用。

sentences.english: However, the imported profile is not "re-imported".
sentences.chinese: 然而，導入的概要文件是不能被再導入的。

sentences.english: The bold line is the link to the person's profile.
sentences.chinese: 加粗的那一行是所搜索對象的概要鏈接。

sentences.english: Create a profile for each bank.
sentences.chinese: 爲每個銀行創建一個概要。

sentences.english: Gain an excellent overview of Summerland Beach.
sentences.chinese: 獲得一個優秀的概要的夏天的海灘。

sentences.english: Otherwise, servers might not be able to access each profile directory.
sentences.chinese: 否則，服務器可能就不能訪問各概要目錄。

sentences.english: A draft of the first basic profile was recently published.
sentences.chinese: 第一個基本概要文件的草案最近已發佈了。

sentences.english: It formulated the concept of profiles to solve this problem and reduce complexity.
sentences.chinese: 它闡明瞭概要的概念以解決該問題和降低複雜性。
